# Build cache + worktrees — never sent to Docker daemon
target/
.worktrees/
**/target/
**/.cosmon/state/
**/.cosmon/archive/

# Git
.git/
.gitignore

# Editors / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# Secrets / local config
.env
.env.local

# Tests / docs (not needed in container build context)
docs/
docs-src/
*.md
!crates/cosmon-rpp-adapter/Dockerfile.md
# cosmon-cli embeds the operator handbook via include_str!, so the `cs`
# build (Dockerfile.strace-test, docker/local-default-container/Dockerfile)
# needs this one doc in the context despite the blanket docs/ exclusion.
!docs/handbook.md
# The spore-e2e image (docker/spore-e2e/Dockerfile) bakes in the TLC seal jar
# and the staged spore (which carries README.md + .md docs) — re-include both
# despite the blanket docs/ and *.md exclusions.
!docs/specs/tla2tools.jar
!docker/spore-e2e/_spore_stage/**
